---
import Layout from "../../components/Layout.astro";
---

<Layout title="GhostFighter Go">
  <section class="project-section">
    <h1>GhostFighter Go</h1>
    <p>Introduction to Systems Development (INF112)</p>
    <p>May 2025</p>
    <img src="/project_photos/ghostfightergo.jpg" alt="Snake Game Screenshot" class="large-project-image" />
    <div class="project-description">
      <p>GhostFighter Go is a project created to learn and apply principles of software development in a team setting. Over the course of the semester, our team of six students, where i had the role of Team Lead, designed, planned, developed, and tested a larger-scale Java game. Through this project, we gained experience with different project methodologies, version control using Git in a collaborative environment, and the complete lifecycle of a software product.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="project-links">
      <a href="https://youtu.be/4XtJXwVUjOk" target="_blank">
        <img src="/logos/yt_logo_text.png" alt="Youtube Demo" class="logo-link" />
      </a>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>

<style>
  .project-section {
    padding: 4rem 1rem;
    background-color: #1e1e24;
    color: #f1f1f1;
    text-align: center;
  }

  h1 {
    font-size: 2.5rem;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
    color: #5DD5FF;
  }

  p {
    font-size: 1rem;
    color: #c4c4c4;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }

  .large-project-image {
    width: 100%; 
    height: auto;
    max-width: 400px;
    border-radius: 8px; 
    margin-bottom: 2rem; 
  }

  .project-description {
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
    font-size: 1.1rem;
  }

  .project-links {
    display: flex;
    justify-content: center;
    gap: 2rem; /* Space between the logos */
  }

  .logo-link {
    width: 80px; /* Adjust the logo size */
    height: auto;
    transition: transform 0.3s ease;
  }

  .logo-link:hover {
    filter: opacity(0.8) drop-shadow(0 0 10px #5DD5FF);
    transform: scale(1.1); /* Scale up the logo on hover */
  }

  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .large-project-image {
      max-width: 100%; /* Allow the image to be responsive */
    }

    .project-section {
      padding: 2rem 1rem; /* Adjust padding for smaller screens */
    }
  }
</style>
